Dear <%= @user.first_name %>,

<% if @method == :cancel %>
Your staffing slot for <%= @staffing.show_title %> on <%= l @staffing.start_time, format: :long %> (<%= @job.name %>) has been removed. A calendar cancellation is attached to this email.
<% else %>
You have been added to staffing for <%= @staffing.show_title %> on <%= l @staffing.start_time, format: :long %> as <%= @job.name %>. A calendar invite is attached: open it to add the event to your calendar.

You can also subscribe to your personal staffing calendar to keep all your shifts automatically in sync. See your account page to find the subscription link.
<% end %>

Regards,

The EUTC Committee
